        <abstract> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Oxalis</hi> plants have arrived safely [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4347</hi>].</p>  
<p>CD regrets his mistake about <hi rend="italic">Disa</hi>; will correct it.</p>  
<p>Thanks RT for his additional facts about <hi rend="italic">Disa</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Is recovering slowly from ten months’ illness.</p> 
<p>Asks whether <hi rend="italic">Strelitzia reginae</hi> grows in gardens at the Cape. Suspects it must be fertilised by a bird.</p> 
        </abstract>
